'''Wyvern Toriq''' was the leader of [[Dragon Squadron]], a group of elite [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] [[T-65 X-wing starfighter/Legends|X-wing]] [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] [[Pilot/Legends|pilots]]. Among his squadron-mates he was considered to be the most "normal" and survived as a result of pure skill, rather than drugs or a psychotic nature as many of the other pilots did.

